title: DDFP 329: Super Bowl diary with Patriots
itunes:title: DDFP 329: Super Bowl diary with Patriots
description:
On part 2 of the NFL podcast crossover, Shek is joined by Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling from the “Around the NFL podcast” to interview Patriots wide receiver Brandon LaFell. Then, Shek breaks down the biggest moments of Super Bowl XLIX alongside Shane Vereen and LeGarrette Blount in Studio 66. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
